    "One of the disadvantages of this preliminary model is the limited size (454 cases) of the data set used.",
    "Further, in the proposed CNN configuration, the training takes approximately two days, even with GPU implementations (Sharma et al. 2017).",
    "Recently in 2023, Tolkach et al.",
    "introduced an AI algorithm designed for tumor tissue detection and tumor regression grading in surgical specimens.",
    "These are obtained from patients diagnosed with oesophageal adenocarcinoma or adenocarcinoma of the oesophagogastric junction (Tolkach et al. 2023)."
